message.entry: Select .NET Core to unload assemblies. To change the environment, restart MATLAB and call 'dotnetenv core'.
The assembly ''{0}'' cannot be unloaded because it is a dependency of the following assemblies:\n{1}\nUnload these assemblies and then call NET.unloadAssembly(''{0}'').
Type ''{0}'' is unavailable because its defining assembly was unloaded.
Input to NET.unloadAssembly must be a string, an instance of ''System.Reflection.AssemblyName'', or instance of ''NET.Assembly''.
Unloading Base Class Libraries is not supported.
